ory for NMR experiments. We\nalso present a theoretical discussion of more exotic states that can be built\nout of the spin and charge order parameters, including spin nematics and phases\nwith `exciton fractionalization'.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Dec 2001 20:27:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 22 Dec 2001 14:32:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 17 Apr 2002 20:57:22 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 7 Sep 2002 15:07:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
